==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Perameles
<hw>Per`a*me"les</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[NL., fr. Gr.
<?/ a pouch + L. <ets>meles</ets> a badger.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<def>Any marsupial of the genus <gen>Perameles</gen>, which includes
numerous species found in Australia. They somewhat resemble rabbits in
size and form. See <xex>Illust.</xex> under
<er>Bandicoot</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

